{
  "stem": "19111.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But you see, the population-- the Polish and the Lithuanian population-- under the German occupation were very hostile to be the Jews for the most part, and it was impossible for the Jews to hide.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Only-- only very few incidents where they were able to find hiding.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They did not want risk their lives, and they didn't give a damn at that point for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- they just didn't extend themselves to a helping hand, even to allow sometimes people to hide for a short time so they can make it to the woods, to the partisans, you know?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And things like that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- there was nowheres to turn to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was nowheres to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did-- did Father David have any communication with you at that time?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Father David-- this is I wanted to tell you-- Father David from the Russian church, somehow he found out-- I guess he surmised that Kailis was where all the furriers were, and he knew that my father was a furrier.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had times-- there were times where people would be walking on the street.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, we had boarded up-- our windows were boarded up, but we had certain openings there, little places where we could look out.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother noticed one day that Father Davis was across the street marching-- walking back and forth in his robes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so, he probably was looking for us, and my mother made a motion to him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Somehow she-- and he came across, and it was lull, a moment, where there were no watchmen at that time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he made contact with-- with us, and he asked--",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
